author: hwright
msg: Fix all of the warnings generated by make 'doc-javahl'.  This does *not* ensure
that the comments are correct, just that they maintain referential integrity
with each other, and don't contain JavaDoc syntax errors.
(doc-javahl): Add a flag to javadoc to allow links for core classes back
to the main documentation on java.sun.com.
Fix sundry syntactic errors in our JavaDocs.
